{"tid":1631093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱睇到隔離Post, 真係唔好亂同穆斯林開玩笑","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:42.000Z","uid":45255,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7381ad8cdbfebd4d8f4b82fb1cd310521988f63","tid":1631093,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1630876\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1630876</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Boyq2aV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoyq2aV.jpg&h=eef2831a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n須知穆斯林係個非常嚴肅嘅宗教，極少甚至接近冇任何言笑<br />\n人地第一次溫馨提示咗唔好亂噴人地神個名喺周圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記著，下不為例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係有心Connect穆斯林、以至Connect到新疆，唔該請先尊重人地嘅宗教文化，基本宗教背景文化最好都應該認識返些少。<br />\n特別是啱啱落實咗反蒙面法而正苦表明穆斯林蒙面不受管制。手足們有手足們照蒙，蒙得幾似都好，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔該千祈千祈唔好喺言談或行為間表達對穆斯林有任何輕挑嘅態度，免得佢地認為我地有意嘲諷甚至侮辱佢哋宗教。</span>切記！<br />\n<br />\nCONNECT人之前，唔該請先認真去尊重人。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！"},{"pid":"8ff5a84618de0046924197ec15688b882ffc7774","tid":1631093,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:18.000Z","msg":"拜託<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f39344103aa4eb1f6a0c45ab93eeefbe5d8a244","tid":1631093,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bd68847dbfbaa068f3ac93053fb37655f40686","tid":1631093,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"你哋係咪唔想要南亞兵？"},{"pid":"3b25d2bca622472c9c0c2a0fe642f66218c6bf03","tid":1631093,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"外國民眾唔會睇得咁深入，通常就睇畫面。勇武形象工程建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628642\" data-auto-lin